#. type: Plain text
#: guix-git/doc/guix-cookbook.texi:578
msgid "You can then happily run"
msgstr "Sie können dann unbesorgt das hier ausführen:"

#.  Do not translate this command
#. type: example
#: guix-git/doc/guix-cookbook.texi:582
